

h3. How to delete files from repo

    delete:  app/view/some/file

<c>git co app/view/some/file
git reset HEAD 
rm app/view/some/file</c>


git rm app/view/somefile

steps
*1 add & commit all files you need to
*checkout deleted file
*reset HEAD of file to untruck it
*now you can reset it




h1. creating aliases

edit @$HOME/.gitconfig@

??[alias]
  cc = commit -m 'Just simple content'
  s = status
  ph = push heroku master??






